==English==

===Noun===
'''vampire''' (plural: ''vampires'')
#a [[mythological]] [[undead]] [[creature]] said to [[feed]] on [[human]] [[blood]]
#a person who [[prey]]s upon others, a [[parasite]]
#a blood-[[suck]]ing [[bat]] ([[vampire bat]])

